name: English Placename Generator
description:
A random English placename generator

I'll add more parts of names when I want.

This isn't a British placename generator, there's nothing Welsh or Irish or Scottish, and it's not particularly Cornish either or Manx, these are just standard English placenames all jumbled up.

It can sometimes generate the names of real places, so if you want to use these names for something make sure you google them first to check that it isn't a real place. A lot of them are already the names of businesses too.

And if you don't know how to pronounce a placename then tough titties figure it out or pay some brits to shout into a microphone for you.
